These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, trike
House: palace, wooden, townhouse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, vegafina, swisher
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, fuchsia, coral
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, dancing
City: edinburgh, berlin, boston
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, may
 1. the person who likes coral is the swisher-smoker##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the person driving the boat is the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 6. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the wooden house is the person driving the trike##1
10. the palace house is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Transport      | boat  | snowmobile   | trike      |
| House          | townhouse      | palace     | wooden     |
| Cigar           | vegafina | swisher  | dunhill   |
| Color   | fuchsia   | coral     | green  |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing      | writing      | dancing      |
| City   | boston      | berlin    | edinburgh   |
| Birthday         | september    | october | may |

