.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, vegafina, swisher
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock, techno
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, cucumber, banana
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, whist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, tulip
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, february
House: cape-cod, wooden, palace
 1. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 9. the palace house is on the far left##1
10. the fan of techno is the person who growsbegonia##1
11. the fan of rock is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar         | vegafina | swisher  | bluemaster     |
| Music-Genre           | hip-hop        | rock | techno    |
| Food   | cucumber  | banana    | pineapple    |
| Game   | whist    | scrabble    | backgammon   |
| Flower           | tulip        | bellflower    | begonia        |
| Birthday         | october     | june  | february     |
| House     | palace         | wooden       | cape-cod |

