.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, zinnia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, dubstep, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, ice-hockey, baseball
House: farmhouse, cottage, townhouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, brown, grey
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, old-henry
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, bridge
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 3. the cottage house is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 6. the townhouse house is the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Flower      | zinnia   | rose         | balloon-flower |
| Music-Genre          | salsa  | dubstep        | metal    |
| Sport           | rowing | ice-hockey  | baseball  |
| House   | townhouse | farmhouse | cottage         |
| Color   | brown | emerald       | grey        |
| Cigar           | dunhill       | ritmeester        | old-henry       |
| Game     | bridge       | mah-jongg  | scrabble       |

