The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, doctor, teacher
House: ranch-style, craftsman, cape-cod
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, prince
 1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the teacher is the person drinking fanta##1
 4. the person playing chess is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 7. the ranch-style house is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 9. the person who growsrose is the doctor##1
10. the person who growsrose is the bluemaster-smoker##1
11. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
12. the person playing chess is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Flower          | daffodil       | aconite   | rose        |
