.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
House: ranch-style, modern, wooden
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, rose
City: london, prague, colone
There 3 different types of food: peas, watermelon, tomato
3 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, frog
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, lavender, orange
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, swisher, siglo
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the wooden house is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the game-smoker is the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person traveling to prague is the owner of the frog##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the modern house##1
10. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
11. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| House      | wooden   | ranch-style        | modern           |
| Flower         | daffodil | rose          | marigold      |
| City           | london   | prague | colone |
| Food   | watermelon  | peas       | tomato         |
| Pet   | cat    | frog          | ferret        |
| Color   | lavender  | orange        | red     |
| Cigar         | game   | siglo         | swisher       |

