The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, dressmaker, doctor
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, may, january
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, skiing, badminton
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, chestnut, orange
 1. the person who likes orange is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the police-officer is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the doctor##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1
11. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1

